  "body": "### Background\r\nOn the token list controller, there is an endpoint used to fetch a list of tokens. Download of the total list is 2.2 Mb of data. After fetching this list, the Mobile app filters this list by duplicate symbols. This process is increasing app load time.\r\n\r\n### Proposed solution\r\nMove the filter logic to the API side. The codefi team has added parameters to enable this. Resulting in a total list of 1000 tokens for 242.8 kb. This will result in a more performative app but also will reduce server costs and less need for the bandwidth for our mobile users.\r\n\r\n### Technical details\r\n- [ ] Update endpoint (TBD)\r\n- [ ] Remove logic to filter tokens",
